Installing eegl:

Be sure you have installed the GNU Scientific Library.

sudo apt-get install libgsl0-dev

Make inst.sh and deinst.sh executable.

chmod 755 inst.sh deinst.sh tstrwlk.sh

Next compile the programs.

./inst.sh

To de-install eegl:

./deinst.sh

To see how to test eegl, read TESTING.
Some of these test programs use new curses and X Windows.

To read about the eegl generator, read README.eegl.
